{"tid":1933603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[1930 民間記者會文字直播]  舊例借屍 污衊抗爭 魔警僭權 律政幫兇","createTime":"2020-03-19T11:18:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T23:35:17.000Z","uid":325953,"like":59,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"abc88414704d1df1e0c1e13f501b49c029eb3b5e","tid":1933603,"uid":325953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T11:18:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jK6oydd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjK6oydd.jpg&h=365aeec3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">舊例借屍 污衊抗爭 <br />\n魔警僭權 律政幫兇</span></strong></span></div><br />\n抗爭運動從六月至今，黑警知法犯法，用各種暴力強行打壓民主聲音。 黑警僭越香港司法制度，近日更串連律政司企圖引用昔日惡法作政治打壓，向國際社會污衊抗爭者，污名化將近一年的民主抗爭，漠視港人追求民主的努力。民間記者會特意邀請眾志國際組成員黃奕武先生及香港人權監察代表葉寬柔小姐，前來講述國際社會對香港民主運動及黑警問題的看法，並講解《反恐條例》等惡法對抗爭者與香港司法制度的潛在影響。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">日期：2020年 3月 19日<br />\n時間：19:30</span><br />\n____________________________<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">大家記得密切留意以下直播平台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n基進報導：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/radicalhk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fradicalhk%2F&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=a3c73a33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/radicalhk/</a><br />\n反送中直播：<a href=\"http://www.hklivegroup.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hklivegroup.com%2F&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=7893bbdc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hklivegroup.com/</a> （首次觀睇需要下載加密插件）<br />\n立場新聞：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2F&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=394dbe74\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/</a><br />\n香港蘋果日報：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2F&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=26af38b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/</a><br />\n香港電台：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FRTHKVNEWS%2F&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=1a985bed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/RTHKVNEWS/</a><br />\nNow新聞：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/now.comNews/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnow.comNews%2F&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=dc8bec51\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/now.comNews/</a><br />\n<br />\n🔈民間記者會現有官方帳號：<br />\nOfficial webpage: <a href=\"http://www.citizenspc.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.citizenspc.org&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=2e33a928\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.citizenspc.org</a><br />\nTG channel: <a href=\"http://t.me/citizenspresscon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fcitizenspresscon&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=a2186bec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/citizenspresscon</a><br />\nFB: <a href=\"http://fb.me/hkercpc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.me%2Fhkercpc&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=63602702\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.me/hkercpc</a><br />\nIG: <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/citizenspresscon\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fcitizenspresscon&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFb3SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=284b79bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/citizenspresscon</a><br />\nYouTube: <a href=\"https://bit